      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "SUBJECT: Reporting of Information on Unconventional Aircraft",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "TO: Commanding Generals, Major Air Commands, ZI and Overseas",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "All United States Air Attaches",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "1. The United States Air Force has a continuing requirement",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "for the reporting and technical analysis of observations of uncon-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "ventional aircraft which might indicate an advance in technological",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "progress of a foreign power. An unconventional aircraft, within",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "the meaning of this directive, is defined as any aircraft or air-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "borne object which by performance, aerodynamic characteristics, or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "unusual features, does not conform to any presently known aircraft",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "type.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "2. It is desired that information on unconventional aircraft",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "be reported in the following manner:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "a. A separate report of each incident will be forwarded.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "No information other than that bearing on the unconventional air-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "craft will be included in this report.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "b. Priority of transmission accorded the report will be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "that appropriate in the judgment of the forwarding agency, accord-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "ing to its apparent authenticity and importance as intelligence.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "c. Reports will be forwarded to Commanding General, Air",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "Materiel Command, Attention: MCIS.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "d. Reports forwarded by electrical transmission will",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "include, as far as possible:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "(1) A brief description of the object(s); its shape,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "size, color, number, formation if more than one,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "aerodynamic features, trail or exhaust, propul-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
